title: Authorizes park police patrols for McCarren, Fort Greene, Commodore John Barry and McGoldrick parks in Brooklyn, Kings county
actClause: AN ACT to authorize the commissioner of the New York city department of parks and recreation to provide for the increased patrol by enforcement officers of McCarren park, Fort Greene park, Commodore John Barry park and McGoldrick park in Brooklyn, Kings county
